portant to check these behaviors to ensure everything functions as expected in signature verification.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented a new dedicated test file for the active class:\n\n- Added `tests/src/com.jcraft/jsch/0.1.27/src/test/java/com_jcraft/jsch/DHGEXTest.java`\n\nThe test exercises `com.jcraft.jsch.DHGEX` through its public `init` and `next` flow:\n\n- Configures `sha-1`, `dh`, and `signature.rsa` implementations through `Session` config.\n- Calls `DHGEX.init(...)`, reaching the `Class.forName` / `newInstance` sites in `init`.\n- Supplies a group-exchange parameters packet and advances state.\n- Supplies a group-exchange reply with an RSA host key and mismatched signature, reaching the `Class.forName` / `newInstance` sites in `next`.\n\nI did not run compile/tests, per workflow instructions.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02a88de5696afdcb016a110c8bf630819d9df7476ef2eb0ef8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 669, "output": 918, "cacheRead": 32768, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34355, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779502206844, "responseId": "resp_02a88de5696afdcb016a110c7f9148819da49fb6a698e2b2be"}}
